{"tid":8510,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[組band]召集所有bass手","createTime":"2016-11-28T11:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T13:13:13.000Z","uid":10923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4ca55235fc8e5eea31296530ed40a9b9af7af3","tid":8510,"uid":10923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"想搵一個bass手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年齡介乎18至24歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樂器程度希望中級到高級 jam到野最好<br />\n<br />\n我地band而家有keyboard 鼓 兩結他一主音<br />\n<br />\n音樂風格 pop rock,core,nu metal<br />\n<br />\n大至上係咁<br />\n但其實乜歌都會玩下 中英日都會玩<br />\n好玩好聽就得<br />\n開波會搵cover show玩<br />\n長遠目標夾順左開始自己租band房搞原創<br />\n到時傾下大家想行咩方向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n非常有心夾好隊band<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我email:<br />\nyoshiki44177@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n有興趣email我 我比我電話你whatsapp慢慢傾<br />\n<br />\n夾band先夾人 最緊要有心!<br />\n傾左唔岩唔緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ca3fe9f0a6a9b75d02d8d741c9f5e9fd376e68","tid":8510,"uid":10923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982221c5f76a19c51adc5b2638e134082ccaac9e","tid":8510,"uid":10923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00abe594c2ca8476b63381ccb3f86dc97e63f3a9","tid":8510,"uid":10923,"like":0,"dislike":0